{"id":156055,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/使solidot更像slashdot/","date":"2011-05-28T21:00:47Z","modified":"2011-05-28T21:00:47Z","title":"使solidot更像slashdot","content":"<p>经测试这个UserCSS可以完美运行在安装了Stylish的Chrome上（在Firefox和Opera上工作不太完美，可能是标准的兼容性问题），能够让solidot摇身一变成slashdot，相对于上一版本有了很大改进，移除了按钮风格，左上角NAZI国徽（更换为我朋友眼眸，时刻叮嘱大家要加油），新增了网址限定，不会与其它网站发生冲突；还可以过滤掉solidot的广告、微博、日志、等很多功能，用了你就离不开它，这是效果图，很不错大家试试吧。是本人闲来无事乱写的，希望高手多提宝贵意见。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/15505c5f/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E4%BD%BFsolidot%E6%9B%B4%E5%83%8Fslashdot&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsolidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F27%2F0950225%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E4%BD%BFsolidot%E6%9B%B4%E5%83%8Fslashdot&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsolidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F27%2F0950225%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101094596351/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/15505c5f/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101094596351/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/15505c5f/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=xTdrgChUqdM:Z4SjCtgGDTY:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=xTdrgChUqdM:Z4SjCtgGDTY:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a